      <title>亨特·拜登枪支指控暂定于六月审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hunter-biden-gun-charges-trial-tentatively-set-for-early-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的儿子亨特将因被控违反联邦枪支法而在六月接受审判。]]></description>
